'''No. 2 (Advanced) Flying Training School''' is a former [[Royal Air Force]] military pilot training school.

==History==
===First formation===
2 Flying Training School (1920-1933 & 1934-1939)
===Second formation===
2 Service Flying Training School (1939-1942)
===Third formation===
2 Flying Training School (1947-1952)
===Fourth formation===
2 Flying Training School (1953-1966)
===Fifth formation===
2 (Basic) Flying Training School (1966-1974)
===Sixth formation===
2 (Advanced) Flying Training School (1976-1997)

The school was disbanded on 30 March 1997 in favour of the civilian operated [[Defence Helicopter Flying School]].{{sfn|Lake|1999|p=104}}

